metadata.name: Generation 1
metadata.description:
Bitcoin - Ordinal 7100

This fusion of AI and manual digital painting is the underpinnings of the "Generations" series. A unique concept driven series to breath life into a new generation of beings forever inscribed on the blockchain.

The art ignites a hope for progress and unity, as it not only captivates with its unique beauty, but also inspires future generations to forge a brighter world.

This work of art boasts a historic provenance that sets it apart from others. The "Pillars" hold the distinction of being one of the first 10,000 ordinal inscriptions on the Bitcoin Blockchain.
